window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I wouldn't consider myself extraordinary.</b></p> <p>That is until my thirtieth birthday when a world I didn't know existed is revealed in a dream. A world where I discover I'm a dragon and the next queen of Arcadia.</p> <p>Me, Cordelia Drake, a soap maker? A queen?</p> <p>Even worse, three men show up claiming I'm the key to saving our realm. A realm that is protected by the balance of a mate bond . . . with them.</p> <p>Can I leave the world I know behind and save a place I've only seen in my dreams?</p> <p>No one told me turning thirty would change everything.</p>"; 
